      <hedline>
        <hl1>Buffalo Is Still in New York</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>''Playoff Hockey to Suit Every Fan Around New York'' (April 12) cites the Devils but not the Buffalo Sabres. Buffalo, while not near Manhattan, is still in New York; New Jersey is not. Some of us New Yorkers also root for the only football team to actually play in the state: the Buffalo Bills.</p>
        <p>David Jelinek  Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
